      "Work where constraint becomes visible taste: compression, on-chain limits, stamp/SVG discipline, small-file decisivene",
      "Images that cost the artist something: risk, restraint, vulnerability, weirdness, refusal of easy polish.",
      "Chain-as-medium thinking: when Tezos, BTC, ETH, or AI/video are not just distribution channels but part of the artwork",
      "Figures and symbols used as vessels rather than mascots: Pepe, masks, guardians, fragments, relics, animals, doubles.",
